video.title: Mountatin Climbers
video.description:
1. Get into a plank position, making sure to distribute your weight evenly between your hands and your toes.

2. Pull your right knee into your chest as far as you can.Switch legs, pulling one knee out and bringing the other knee in.

3. Keep your hips down, run your knees in and out as far and as fast as you can. Alternate inhaling and exhaling with each leg change.
